posting_body: ['Apartment 306', '38 Dolores', '38 Dolores St, San Francisco, CA, 94103', 'Use this link for more information:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 61', 'OR Text', '61', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team.', 'The Greater Good: 38 Dolores', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1330 Sq.', 'Ft.', '38 Dolores embraces a green lifestyle where community wellness comes full circle.', 'Living walls are your art work; Whole Foods Market, your downstairs kitchen; Dolores Park, your backyard.', "It's a philosophy of focusing on the greater good, for yourself and your neighbors.", '**Pictures are a mix of different layouts, may not be of actual unit**', '**Prices of homes are subject to change, please contact property for most up to date pricing and availability**', 'Features', '- Recess Medicine Cabinet', '- Moen Fixtures', '- Studio Becker European Cabinets™', '- Private Balconies*', '- Soaking Tub', '- Frameless Glass Shower Enclosures', '- Granite Counter Tops', '- Programmable Thermostat', '- Floor to Ceiling Windows', '- Roller Shades', '- European Plumbing Fixtures', '- WiFi in Common Areas', '- Panoramic Views of the City*', '- Quartz Countertops*', '- Pre-Wired for TV, Internet (Fiber), and Telephones', '- Private Balcony*', '- Washer Dryer', "- 11' Ft. Volume Ceilings*", '- Wood Floors', '- Stainless Steel Appliances with Gas Range', '- Natural Stone Vanity Countertops', '*in select units', 'Community Amenities', '- Bike Storage Room', '- Outdoor Social Fire Pit', '- Secured Parking Garage - Assigned Parking Space $425/mo', '- Community Clubroom/Hosting Room', '- Rental Storage Lockers', '- Dry Cleaning & Laundry Service (Additional Costs)', '- Eco Roof', '- Outdoor Herb Garden', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet Rent: $75/month for dogs under 75 lbs; $100 for dogs over 75 lbs; $50/month for up to 2 cats.', 'Pet rent covers two pets, i.e. if an applicant has two cats, we would only charge $50.', 'If an applicant has 2 different type of pets we only charge one pet rent which will always default to the greater amount.', '- Pet Deposit: There is a $500 deposit per pet.', 'This becomes part of the residents total security deposit and will not be refundable until the resident moves out.', '-There is a maximum of 2 pets allowed per apartment', 'Income Requirements:', 'Applicants must have a combined income requirement of 3x the rent.', '1eOtDyITz']
